I may start writing in this thing once again.  I made it a LONG time ago and I've looked through the old posts a time or two.  I miss writing, I seem like I never get a chance too. Like right now I should be downstairs helping Ronn and my mom, but I don't want to.  She always bitches.  I'm so beyond sick of getting bitched at.  Ronn used to be on my side like all the time, now he takes hers.  Maybe I am crazy, maybe I do act like a kid, but it's hard to act grown up when you're treated like a kid.  I which my dukkie icon on here was blue!  That's random but still I made it before I had photoshop on here I'm sure because I would've altered or even changed my picture by now.  Alyx is sleeping, and so is Zaya, and since I haven't wrote in forever, I don't know if I ever even mentioned them.  Zaya's my two year old, and Alyx is my almost 7 month old.  Ronn's my boyfriend of 3yrs.  I feel so like shit right now, just been feeling like I want to cry.  Can't figure out why tho, pms already passed, so it can't be that.  Maybe my brain really is off-balanced.  I do know that I should go see a doctor, regardless of Ronn's ultimatium.  I just don't got the guts.  I finally had the guts to try to get back into Job Lot and I haven't gotten a call back.  Guess it didn't look as good as I thought.  Oh well, there are other jobs...I just don't feel like starting from sratch again.  If I didn't have that cyst, I would still be working there I'm sure, and I wouldn't have had to have that surgery.  My brain is fried.  I don't really even know what Ronn or my mom is doing.  I just know they are not up here.  I'm almost afraid to go find out.  I want to help but I don't at the same time.  It's not because I'm lazy, it's cuz I don't want to hear it.  Zaya's been up my ass all day, she finally went to bed.  I think they just came upstairs with something.  Wow I haven't done a real journal entry like this in such a long time.  It's more like my sanity notes that I needed to write in high school to survive.  I need to find a shrink, but I'm kinda afraid to do that too.  I don't know what they would say to me, and I don't know if I want to hear it.  Sometimes it really is like I'm two different people, one's a bitch, one's not, but no matter who I am I get yelled at just the same.

The TV is running in the background as I type.  Food Network is on, it's my favorite alternative to everything else on TV, most of the time.  I can hear movement downstairs, it's my mom and Ronn.  Moving stuff I'm sure.  I'm not sure how much more they can be doing down there.  Kelli's sleeping, so are my kids.  My right foot is resting on the computer desk's lower shelf, and my left is perched on the plastic piece above the chair's wheels.  I lick my lips because their chapped.  My throats been sore for a while, due to the fact that I haven't been able to breathe out of my nose in a while.  I get cotton-mouth when I sleep, it's real bad sometimes.  Water seems to soothe it good, but there's not enough mouthwash in the world to get me feeling like my mouth doesn't reak.  Well gtg I can't help but want to kno what they are doing downstairs.  BBL maybe.

I don't know why but I posted last nite and it didn't work.  Something to do with my popup blocker.  Anyways I'm sure I won't write as much as I did yesterday or even in as much detail but here goes nothing.  First off I slept until 1:30 this afternoon and that's not that unusual, I hate it, I feel so useless.  I don't even help Ronn out with the baby in the morning for the most part because I'm soo tired.  I talked to the doctor and they don't think anything of it.  I think it's from like depression, but why should I be sad right?  I have everything going for me ::coughyearightcough::  I work at Job Lot making more than I would make if I worked for my father I just came to find out, and I couldn't work full time there either, but yet after all his offers I was finally thinking of going up there so we could almost completely get away.  Right now I'm exhausted, and why I've done nothing all day, it's 4 in the afternoon and I've only been up for like what 2&1/2 hours.  I was going to go to the store for my mom to get them ice cream but I told them the only way I would go is if I had some of my own money to buy things, she asked how much I wanted and I said how much do you have, big mistake.  I said fine 20 or 40 bucks and she handed me fourty goes to hand me another 20 and says get the ice cream and some of those frozen pizzas (u kno the small individual ones)  I'm like mom that's at Stop 'n Shop and she's like oh nevermind, fumbles around with her money and then puts her purse away, i'm like I still need money, she goes you got some I said what I'm supposed to be buying your ice cream for you?  She's like why not I buy everything else you eat in this house, i'm like yea but why would I buy 2 things of ice cream I'll waste all my money.  Anyways it was a stupid conversation that ended up with me coming downstairs and typing this.

Have you ever wanted something so bad you can't help but cry, because you know you can't have it. I hate Christmas (and I wasn't talking about wanting a present) Some of the holidays are horrible when you're not with anyone... I had myself convinced for some long damn time I don't need anyone... but it's so hard when you know what you want, who you want. I love my sleep, but I hate my dreams... I have great dreams, but then I wake up to my fucked up reality. My mom would rather me live on the street than in the house right now, my dad can't wait until he wastes all his money for my to (not purposely) fail out of college, my step dad likes to be on my side until ANYONE else is around, my sister thinks I'm made of money and time (wanting me to go to Tennessee for Christmas), my friends... well what I have left of them, barely talk to me, we barely do anything. My job, it sucks, I don't like alot of the people there and I don't think I have been through one day there without getting mad at someone or me thinking someones mad at me. I feel like all my work is doing nothing because I don't have that much money (in the bank-quote unquote) and I need my recent paychecks for car insurance, gas money, and Christmas present money. I wish I could just sleep it all away, slip into unreality for a while, but that's not possible. I like someone who I'm pretty sure doesn't like me back and because of the situation between us it's not very easy to find things like that out. God it hurts, it really does, and I hate to cry but I think I NEED to. I haven't been able to write poetry for some time because I have no muse...or no new situation for my muse maybe. And I haven't been able to write stories either because well, time, and because I can't think straight, everything is blocked and clogged on my mind and I wish I could just drift away and get it to go away so I can think or rather imagine clearly without interuptions... its fucking like watching tv and having an infomercial pop on in the climax of the show, and when the show comes back it's over. I need to get moving on my own and I know I'm not ready, but the time has come and I can't figure out how to stall any longer. I need help, but I can't find it myself or in myself. I feel like I fell overboard off a boat and i'm drowning, I can see the livesaver ring but I can't reach it, and my mom won't throw it to me. I need time to think and w/e, by myself, but there is no by myself in this house and there is no me time because there is nowhere to go. There is no one to talk to either, Jill, her problems are far worse, Meg, won't understand, Craig, I put him through enough shit already, Keith, wouldn't understand either... it's harder than it sounds... and there really is no one but them. I think I'm just gonna park somewhere tomorrow and sit in my car and think. (I'll bring my notebook incase any ideas or anything flow, but there really is nowhere even to park. I know I'm lame, I know I'm not so smart when it comes to certain things, but I dunno, I just know I need the me time. I wish I had someone to talk to tho, I really miss it. (I want a theripst, but my mom don't give two shits) I need to make this pain go away, I hate to live it and I want it gone. It's like being born without arms and having an itch on your back. You would like to itch it yourself but you know you need some help.

"...Then, then she punched me in the stomach and I doubled over in pain.  When I was down I went for her legs, you know, to try and knock her down and she backed up a bit and kicked me hard twice in the ribs.  I'm pretty sure they are atleast bruised. At this point I should've been in tears, but, but I wasn't, I was going slow but I was gradually picking myself off the floor.  She grabbed me, by the neck and my lower shirt and slammed me into the wall and I fell; blood was dripping consistantly now from the cut above my puffy, black and blue eye.  Still not a tear would cascade itself down my cheek.  I used the wall for support and as she was laughing I stood myself up; still I did not want a fight, and I kept asking myself why and how I got into this situation.  Before the thoughts had time to pass through my mind I ran at her full force and tackled her to the ground, she still laughed saddistically and so I forced myself with all my self control not to hit her.  I was enraged and because alreadyhit so many times and using all my self control I was easily knocked over.  Now she was on the top and I was getting punched.  Finally, I let my hand form a fist and it collided with her jaw.  She looked suprised asa she wiped the blood from her chin.  I forced her off of me and slowly contently, feeling lost, insecure, and very doubtful I turned away.  She grabbed at my back with less power than her previous attacks, and I clenched a fist so tight I thought my knuckles would bleed, and I slammed it into the glass door beside me.  My hand was cut open in several places and glass poured down like rain.  I grabbed my right hand with my left held it to my chest.  Pain seared throughout my body and I slid myself down the wall, 'You cannot defeat me,' I said, 'only I...can defeat me." And with that last word I closed my tearfilled eyes and felt no pain."  "That didn't really happen!" "Yeah, but that's what it feels like..."

Well I wonder if anyone will read this.  I almost forgot to update.  Nothing really has been happening, my life is boring, lol.  I can't wait to get my license on Thursday, but I'm really nervous, everything is depending on me getting that license.  I need to get to work, and wherever else and no one knows for sure if I'll even pass the stupid test.  I mean I know it's easy, but I know how I am when I get anxious.  It feels so weird, everyone is starting school, but me.  Well and a couple people I know, but like Jill's started, Megean's starting, and yea everyone else.  God my life is really boring, I was sitting at work about to leave and I was thinking to myself like, "geez, the sadest part about tonite is it's gonna be like every other nite, i'm going to go home and go on the computer right when i do and be on it until forever at nite....I'm pathetic."  I am also too lazy to get any of my cd's out so I keep listening to the only good song I d/led (down w/the sickness - disturbed) over and over again.  (I never get sick of disturbed)  I really got to remember to pick up an application for Megean tomorrow, and I have to remember that I can't stay home on Thursday cuz I need to talk to Valerie (my boss) about working full time.  Not that I really wanna work full time lol, but there's nothing else to do, Xspecially when everyone else is in school.  (I wonder if Dez is starting in the Fall?) BRB I gtpee.  Well I wasn't too lazy to pee, but then again, I really had to go.  Oh yea earlier I was on www.your-poetry.com (my s/n on it is cold, incase you wanna read anything), I used to go there alot more, but since my computer died I hadn't been there.  I read some of my poems and like three of them I totally didn't remember lol.  Oh well.  I was thinking about writing some poems tonite, but somewhere along the line I lost my inspiration, but who knows, I still have time.  I mean it's only 2am.  I was up until 345 last nite (well day w/e) and then i didn't wake up until 1245 that afternoon.  It was pretty sucky lol, don't get me wrong I love my sleep, but I hate when everyone else is awake but me.  Alright I'm gonna go to bed now. (I still need to finish proofreading one of my stories I'm writing, it's kinda stupid I think, but then again I wrote it, and besides if you read anything like a million times it's boring and horrible.) lol byes
